--Q
jabberd: error while loading shared libraries: libjabberd.so.2: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory
--A
$ ldd /usr/local/bin/jabberd
	linux-vdso.so.1 =>  (0x00007fff18f43000)
	libjabberd.so.2 => not found
$ whereis libjabberd.so.2
libjabberd.so: /usr/local/lib/libjabberd.so.2 /usr/local/lib/libjabberd.so
$ 将/usr/local/lib/添加到 $LD_LIBRARY_PATH 路径(.bashrc)
